#, no-wrap
msgid "Upgrading to v1.7"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: UG9/en/linstor-kubernetes-upgrade-guide.adoc:234
#: UG9/en/linstor-kubernetes-upgrade-guide.adoc:308
